compat_comments:
Fully completed.

Game is playable with good speed with various graphical glitches:
- Main menu is slow
- Glitchy outlines on distant elements covered by fog (noticeable in the second town);
- Z-ordering issues (some places look like they are flooded, especially in later stages);
- Characters have black splotches and randomly flash in green (the fix has been found and just need to be merged);
- Some major slowdowns occur during the last parts of the game (sometimes close to 10-15fps).

Shadows/broken pause menu backgrounds are now fixed.

Music both in race and in the main menu is perfect;
The Framerate is not stable in the main menu but you can easily navigate through it.
In the garage and showroom the framerate drops depending on how many objects appears on screen;
Any type of mode is unplayable (Race and Time Attack) due to the low framerate even when you are the only car on track;
Not any graphical issue at all apart from the licenses plates during a race;
the Geometry Wars minigame runs perfect with no issues at all.
